ws|BOL News (4K)]]\n* [[Business Plus (TV Channel)|Business Plus]]\n* [[Capital TV (Pakistan)|Capital TV]]\n* [[Channel 5 (Pakistan)|Channel 5]]\n* [[City 41]]\n* [[City 42]]\n* [[Dawn News]]\n* [[Din News|Din News HD]]\n* [[Dunya News]]\n* [[Express News (Pakistan)|Express News]]\n* [[Geo News]]\n* [[Geo Tez]]\n* [[GNN (news channel)|GNN (HD)]]\n* [[Hum News|Hum News (HD)]]\n* [[Lahore News|Lahore News (HD)]]\n* [[Neo TV|Neo TV HDc]]\n* [[News One]]\n* [[PTV News]]\n* [[Samaa TV]]\n* [[SUCH TV|Such TV]]\n* [[Public News Pakistan|Public News (HD)]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Sindhi News====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Daily Awami Awaz|Awami Awaz TV]]\n* [[KTN News]]\n* [[Sindh TV News]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Pushto News====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Khyber News]]\n* [[Mashriq TV]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====Balochi News====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[VSH News]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====English News====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[BBC South Asia]]\n* [[Indus News|Indus News (4K)]]\n* [[PTV World]]\n\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Sports===\n\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Geo Super]]\n* [[PTV Sports]]\n* [[Ten Sports Pakistan]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Children's===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Cartoon Network vs tn(Pakistan)|Cartoon Network]]\n* [[Nickelodeon Pakistan]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Movies===\n\n====Urdu Movies====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Filmazia]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n====English Movies====\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Music===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[8XM]]\n* [[ARY Musik]]\n* [[Jalwa]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Health===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n*None right now\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Food===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Hum Masala]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Education===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Raah TV]]\n* [[Virtual University of Pakistan|Virtual University]] VU 1, VU 2,VU 3,VU 4\n{{div col end}}\n\n===Business===\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Business Plus (TV Channel)|Business Plus]]\n{{div col en